{"tid":845624,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【偶像明星運動會】Irene射箭直穿鏡頭驚呆全場！","createTime":"2018-10-02T22:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T16:14:17.000Z","uid":34643,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"01b71a1714d176fd5a0b2ff9d6f1085e7ff9f8d4","tid":845624,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T22:00:32.000Z","msg":"韓國MBC電視台一年兩度的特備節目《偶像明星運動會》，歷年來非常受粉絲和觀眾歡迎，每逢農曆新年、中秋節都會舉行，昨晚（26日）最新一屆戰況播出，不過於射箭環節起了一場小騷亂，到底怎麼回事？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/ming_pao_weekly_776/ddf03d8df4e7c910c88d6e355ac905de\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fming_pao_weekly_776%2Fddf03d8df4e7c910c88d6e355ac905de&h=0be2d302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m8hjydGC_64\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dm8hjydGC_64&d=iUr0gEzqSs0uuOOQL8Ar1JZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=9eafd962\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m8hjydGC_64</a><br />\n<br />\n原來，女團Red Velvet成員Irene跟gu9udan世正出戰女子團體弓箭決勝局，原本叮噹碼頭的分數令現場觀眾和攝影棚裡的主持人非常緊張，怎料此時Irene射出一箭，所有人都驚呆了！她的箭直接把節目組設置在箭靶正中心的鏡頭射穿，發出清脆的鏡頭爆破聲，瞬間失去畫面，連Irene本人都一陣驚慌失笑！不過，雖然Irene完美射出10分佳績，但最終金牌還是由對手gu9udan贏得，可惜！"},{"pid":"279489fe93c6e9815e224e493bbb322fd831eecf","tid":845624,"uid":34643,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T22:03:06.000Z","msg":"老肉 vs 黑肉"},{"pid":"20395283cfc5e1e3ef81b6d47a488e9117f5bf7a","tid":845624,"uid":555,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T22:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cfile6.uf.tistory.com/image/998370405BAA1CF2014A42\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile6.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F998370405BAA1CF2014A42&h=99ed73a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cfile4.uf.tistory.com/image/99B884335BAA21EE26705A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile4.uf.tistory.com